As you can see, project management

4
00:00:14,810 --> 00:00:16,750
transcends all industries.

5
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:19,290
Projects can be large or small.

6
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:22,000
They can be fairly simple and straightforward, or quite

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,010
complex and time consuming.

8
00:00:24,010 --> 00:00:26,180
You can initiate them yourself or you

9
00:00:26,180 --> 00:00:27,960
can be given a project to complete

10
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,830
without having much experience.

11
